<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.9">
<l>kuṭaiyum ceruppum koṭātētā mōtara ṉaināṉ</l>
<l>uṭaiyum kaṭiya ṉavuṉṟu vemparaṟ kaḷuṭai</l>
<l>kaṭiyaveṅ kāṉiṭaik kālaṭi nōvakkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>koṭiyēṉeṉ piḷḷaiyaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I didn’t give a parasol and leather sandals to Dāmodara,</l>
<l>[yet] this cruel woman, sent my child after the calves</l>
<l rend="indent">in the harsh, hot forest</l>
<l>with broken, sharp, painful, hot stones</l>
<l>so that [now his] leg and feet ache.</l>
<l>Ah! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
